text: Léonard Dutz (born 6 August 1947) is a Belgian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Belgium Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kelmis
